2. git add .

  hello.hava
  age.java

git add hello.java

- add files for tracking

3. git commit -m "Fixing a payment bug"

-----------

4.git remote add origin https://github.com/thecodevillage/java-core-intro-c2.git


5. git push -u origin master - move local changes to remote server

6. git pull origin master - move remote changes to local server
